WEBVTT

1
00:50:25.920 --> 00:50:32.080 
一切都始于赞美 承诺和恩惠 这是我们彼此的需求
It begins with praise, promises, favours. It is their need and ours.

2
00:50:32.450 --> 00:50:34.970 
然后某一天 他们会改变规则
Then one day, they change the rules.

3
00:50:35.160 --> 00:50:39.480 
我们之间再无瓜葛 只剩猜忌
No more business between us. Just suspicion.

4
00:50:40.180 --> 00:50:41.180 
审问
Interviews.

5
00:50:41.700 --> 00:50:43.040 
隔阂
Isolation.

6
00:50:44.600 --> 00:50:46.880 
我们不能给他们任何借口
We must give them no excuses!

7
00:50:46.880 --> 00:50:49.520 
给谁呀 傻婆子
Give who, you silly old biddy?

8
00:50:49.520 --> 00:50:51.510 
当然是纳粹
The Nazis, of course.

